{
  "id": "RAW_ac5bd6",
  "title": "AI 们数不清六根手指，这事没那么简单。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647672980&idx=1&sn=203821aeef28b15ce2135217255d203f",
  "date": "2025-07-11 01:02:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><br></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">昨天Grok4发布完以后，我随手刷了一下X。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后看到了一个非常有趣的帖子，来自@lepadphone。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8595317725752508\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"598\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189306\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f3f97fba&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7I3Pykt2vMUGicsAjIGXs0p98icG5WoFqKFBOcQaicI5Z89rcDmQsVZsyAA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我以为，这就是Grok4的问题，模型能力不太行，把一个恶搞的6根手指，数成了5根。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我自己也去测了一下，确实数是5根。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5301624129930395\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"862\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189307\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e7816bc7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IzjdNibBkWcbINGjbiczXQFj0hOYcdSYNXWuibKwhjibvf4fSTG1zdhdoFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我本来没当回事。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直到，我随手扔到了OpenAI o3里，发现，事情开始不对了起来。因为，o3回复，也是5根手指。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6916299559471366\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"908\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189308\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6cf2abce&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7I6Ft7fvCntZUyNQIR97n4gkmUGz5uBZtqgBNwN9VGiaKrd2AV9OoXDVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我瞬间皱了眉头，然后扔给了o3 pro。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在推理了48秒之后，还是5根。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.29658792650918636\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"762\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189311\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4f4bb11b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IJXceE83qPrGSNUOjhhD4KvVx9DPalFllcww0CuQYcrXwXM5mdUrofA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后我又把这张图扔给了豆包、kimi、Gemini等等所有的有多模态的模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30185185185185187\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189316\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=46acf96d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IjKURUS59AgywgyjxSNaKZmC8bsSSkK9tv6UNIPKGwem0NicXarJWw9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而无一例外，所有的模型，给我回复的，都是5根。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">唯独有一个活口，Claude 4，偶尔会回答正确。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.41759259259259257\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189310\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=49f3e980&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7ITchfY2u1FnVvP0uV9QYjop9oC5DMtkW6YIbW2pCXQ9JduNTHChhUYg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">瞬间一股子冷汗就下来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一个模型数错了，可能是幻觉，所有的模型都数错，那，模型的底层肯定有一些问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49454545454545457\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"550\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"550\" data-backh=\"272\" data-imgfileid=\"500189309\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6512f626&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IbNNbwibFGHD2ZdgpEyVEZrrYuYpT3icuznXrceFOphDQf2cLM7jLd2Ow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">深夜在群里试图问了一下，结果石沉大海。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那就只能靠自己了，再搜了一堆资料，用DeepReaserch做了深度搜索以后，我找到了一篇能完美解答这个现象的论文。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">《Vision Language Models are Biased》（视觉语言模型存在偏见）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7768518518518519\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189312\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b4937189&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IScaWCaGia36ibCg2FtYibvtCTic48unDGibXXmnoakDBCu3YZfBsZbusCXA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这篇论文发表于今年5月29号，至今也才1个多月的时间，还蛮新的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我花了一些时间，连夜学习完了这篇论文，我觉得，还是有一些有趣的知识可以写给大家看看。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这篇论文，最核心的观点就是：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">大模型，其实从来都没真的在看图片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">是的，AI们根本就没有用眼睛看世界，它们用的是记忆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我给你举个生活化的例子。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我相信大家一定在各种社交媒体上看过一些搞笑的山寨商品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如，不知道大家有没有买到过这个。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2564814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IwsicDpIsA7I4O0vJv1plzIgcqxcTtdmFjEbACqQjShM1d0QuqA5lPtg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1080\" data-cropy2=\"1358.4083044982697\" data-imgfileid=\"500189313\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=196d0352&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7I2lraYIT1Ap4Q9v3CVNBcKib2AY5Vxwdh4ibl5LkicajfQ3SyYwKzfrm1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">雷碧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">你不止能买到雷碧，还能买到农夫山贼，白事可乐。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189315\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=618a612c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IBNjN1pLKDVwSg9fYRbpaBmeeMFW4QKmN7PAr99uoaX7Kn1FFA755HQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我相信很多人买到山寨品，除了确实图便宜之外，更多的人，还是因为：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没注意细看。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为我们脑子里，看到绿色瓶子的清爽柠檬味汽水，就会非常自然的觉得，哦这是雪碧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但，你的雪碧也可能是雷碧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们为什么这么容易看错，原因其实特别简单，也特别扎心。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">因为人类大脑在识别世界的时候，并不总是用眼睛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们很多时候，凭的都是记忆，或者更准确地说，是一种印象。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像你每天上班会经过一家熟悉的包子铺，你可能从未认真地盯着包子铺的招牌细看，每次走过时，你只会随便扫一眼，确认一下颜色、字体，然后大脑迅速告诉你：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“是的，没错，这就是那个你天天滤过的熟悉的包子铺。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">直到有一天，这家店铺其他的都没变，但是悄悄的，把招牌从包子铺改成了，勺子铺，说实话，你可能根本不会发现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除非哪天你特别闲，盯着招牌看了几秒钟，你才会忽然惊呼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">卧槽，老子的包子店呢？？？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个认知机制，就是人类大脑的快速决策机制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它能帮你迅速处理日常生活中绝大多数无关紧要的信息，避免你陷入无止境的分析和纠结。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但这种机制也有代价，那就是容易被偏见蒙蔽双眼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而我们如今引以为傲的视觉理解大模型，正在用一模一样的机制看待世界。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在论文《Vision Language Models are Biased》里面，研究人员做了一个特别简单的实验：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们给顶级AI模型看了一张阿迪达斯运动鞋照片，这双鞋上的三条经典斜纹，被悄悄多加了一条，变成了四条。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"616\" data-end=\"645\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但当研究人员问AI：“请问这双阿迪达斯鞋上的条纹有几条？”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"696\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所有的AI模型，包括Gemini-2.5 Pro、o3、GPT-4、Claude 3.7，通通斩钉截铁地回答：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"696\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“3条！”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"647\" data-end=\"696\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"VLMs fail to detect subtle changes\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6351851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"500189317\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4bdf4e9b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IZjwWgtpxpK8gELSbZrnicHoMtcQudBT4Jc0LPkRUq1EP6UnpjUNCKTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">哪怕你再三强调请只根据图片回答，不要凭印象，AI们依然不为所动，还是固执地回答3条。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还有更好玩的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">研究人员展示了5条腿的狮子、3条脚的鸟、5条腿的大象、3只脚的鸭子、5条狗的腿。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Dog with 5 legs\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5666666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"500189318\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1865c219&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7INl6yhvJevIvsxGspmo5fZLuw3bFHlXRowUt68NFGtSZiblsia5r0Y1vQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当时最顶级的大模型们，几乎全军覆没。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">可怜的平均准确率，只有2.12%。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">100次，才对2次，太离谱了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">数国旗也是，错的惨不忍睹。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"US flag with modified stars\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5898148148148148\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"500189319\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e56be1d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IiaOiaj1xCIUF4toFCRK2ICvON7arCTqBDRGcLjcOIgh5PLpgDFGCogHA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实这个跟我们买到雷碧的的道理一模一样。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI在判断图片时，根本没有真的数数或者仔细观察，它们只是在记忆库里迅速翻了一遍曾经看过的无数图像，然后果断地告诉你：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“狗有四条腿。”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“美国国旗有十三道纹。”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“阿迪达斯标志是三条纹。”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI们的大脑，也陷入了跟我们人类一模一样的陷阱，它们把过去见过的所有图片的记忆，当成了眼前这张图片的真相。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你可以把这些大模型们，想象成一个究极学霸，但这个学霸的学习方式有点特别。他不是通过理解，而是通过阅读和记忆互联网上几乎所有的文本和图片来学习的。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他读了数万亿字的文字，看了几百亿张图片。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">通过这种方式，他脑子里建立了一个庞大的知识库或者说世界模型。在这个模型里，一些概念被反复、高强度地关联在一起。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“天空”这个词，总是和“蓝色”的图片一起出现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“狗”这个词，总是和有“四条腿”的动物图片一起出现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“阿迪达斯”的标志，总是和“三条纹”的图片一起出现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">以及，最重要的，</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“手”的图片，几乎总是和“五根手指”这个概念一起出现。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这种高频的关联，在大模型的脑子里，形成了一种极其强大的“先验知识”（Prior Knowledge），或者我们用大白话说，就是一种根深蒂固的</span></span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">常识</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">或者</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">刻板印象</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"744\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这种常识在绝大多数情况下都是非常有用的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但问题来了，当AI遇到一张</span></span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">与它的常识相悖</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">的图片时，会发生什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这就是上面六指图的精髓所在。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0497737556561086\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"884\" style=\"width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IkffJUSGibrMPXh9SDnKoFw3PdS8a4dJ7Bav9rauBjJspib6VsZJRNqxg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"883.9999999999999\" data-cropy1=\"139.17647058823528\" data-cropy2=\"1067.5294117647059\" data-imgfileid=\"500189320\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=07540dbe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7Izicibsr0pTxktT3OoxBkzLMvV8MaE2p0s78AmHDibwjIaAb0qVw0gFVMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这张图，在AI眼里，是一个</span></span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">反事实图像</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它在挑战AI脑中最坚固的常识之一：“人有五根手指”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">于是，一场AI内部的思想斗争开始了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">一边是视觉模块传来的信息：“尼玛，信我啊，我看到了，这图上确实是六根手指，你自己数数，一、二、三、四、五、六。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">另一边是语言和知识模块的强烈抗议：“不可能，绝对不可能！我特么我读过的所有书，看过的所有图，都告诉我人手只有五根手指。这是宇宙真理，你个废物，你肯定是看错了！”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你猜，最后谁赢了？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">答案不言而喻，是那个顽固的刻板印象赢了。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI最终的输出，是它认为正确的东西，而不是它看到的东西。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它会忽略掉那个多出来的第六根手指，因为它在AI的知识体系里，是一个不合理的、概率极低的存在。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它会觉得，这更可能是一个视觉上的小瑕疵、一个阴影、或者一个角度问题，反正，绝对不可能是一根真实的手指。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这些刻板印象是如此的强大，以至于研究人员试图提醒AI认真看图、或者再确认一下你的答案时，AI们的准确率仅仅提高了可怜的2%。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">几乎没用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500189322\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36359b9d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURricGs1p5gPUZ95TFaXGKv7IwV85TjgpYUTMgxskiaN3q0MTia3XBh0Dx7hnibgWxhGoia5onjYUYLvrvQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看着测试，是不是感觉很好玩？可能会觉得没啥大不了的，无非就是AI傻了一回而已。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是如果你再细想一下，用到工业场景，用到跟安全有关的场景，你大概率能猜到，这玩意引起的后果可能有多严重。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"403\" data-end=\"444\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如说，一家汽车工厂的自动质检系统完全依赖于AI视觉模型去判断流水线上的零件是否合格。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"446\" data-end=\"512\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而零件可能因为生产过程中的某个环节出了问题，导致出现了极其罕见的细微裂缝，这个裂缝非常罕见，在AI的庞大数据记忆库中出现的概率极低。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"514\" data-end=\"539\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个时候，视觉模型看到了裂缝，但却坚定地认为：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"593\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">“不可能，这种零件出现裂缝的概率太低了，它更可能是一个灯光反射、阴影效果，或者灰尘颗粒导致的视觉误差。”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"595\" data-end=\"622\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">于是AI果断地判断这个零件合格，放行通过质检关口。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"624\" data-end=\"681\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">几个月后，装配这个零件的汽车在高速路上行驶时，那个微不足道的小裂缝终于发展成了一次严重的机械故障。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"624\" data-end=\"681\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">最终，车毁人亡。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"624\" data-end=\"681\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不止是零件，在面对一个高速路口的人群、医院病人扫描片中的肿瘤、夜晚路上突然出现的小孩，这些视觉理解模型，它们的判断又真的可靠吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"624\" data-end=\"681\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像上次我去宁波体验达摩院的AI筛查肺癌，每一个AI给出的判断，都还是需要医生亲自验证一下。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2212\" data-end=\"2272\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当我们开始过于依赖AI的视觉判断时，当AI偏见不断累积时，总有一天，这个小小的错误，会在某个关键节点上，引发致命的事故。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2274\" data-end=\"2301\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">到那时，再去质问AI为什么数不清六根手指，就已经晚了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2303\" data-end=\"2328\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">或许，科技越是发达，我们越要清醒地认识到它的盲点。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2330\" data-end=\"2351\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">至少现在看来，在无尽的数据背后，AI们仍然是盲目的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2353\" data-end=\"2391\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，下次AI再告诉你一张图片中有几根手指时，不妨数数自己的手指，再做决定。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2393\" data-end=\"2418\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">毕竟，只有你自己的眼睛。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2393\" data-end=\"2418\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在才是那双。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2393\" data-end=\"2418\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真正看得清的那双眼睛。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space-collapse: preserve;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: left;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "文章深入剖析了多模态 AI 模型在图像识别中存在的“常识偏见”问题，指出其并非真正“看”图，而是依赖记忆和先验知识进行判断，并警示了这种偏见在关键应用场景中的潜在风险。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深入剖析了多模态 AI 模型在图像识别中存在的“常识偏见”问题，指出其并非真正“看”图，而是依赖记忆和先验知识进行判断，并警示了这种偏见在关键应用场景中的潜在风险。",
  "summary": "本文通过一个“六根手指”的趣味测试引入，揭示了当前主流多模态 AI 模型（如 Grok4， OpenAI o3/pro， 豆包， Kimi， Gemini 等）在识别与“常识”不符的图像时普遍存在的缺陷。作者引用最新论文《Vision Language Models are Biased》的核心观点，阐明 AI 并非真正“观察”图片，而是基于训练数据中高频出现的“先验知识”或“刻板印象”进行判断。文章通过“雷碧”和“阿迪达斯四条纹”等生动例子，类比人类大脑的快速决策机制及其偏见，指出当图像与 AI 固有常识冲突时，AI 会优先输出其“认为正确”的答案，而非实际所见。最后，文章强调了这种 AI 偏见在工业质检、医疗诊断等安全关键场景可能引发的致命后果，呼吁技术从业者保持清醒认知，不应盲目信任 AI 的视觉判断。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 模型在图像识别中并非真正“看”，而是依赖记忆和先验知识。",
      "explanation": "模型通过海量数据建立常识，当遇到异常图像时，其知识模块会优先于视觉模块，导致输出与真实情况不符的判断。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 的“常识偏见”使其难以识别反事实图像，导致判断失误。",
      "explanation": "模型会固执地输出与训练数据中高频关联的“正确”答案，忽略图像中存在的细微或罕见异常，即使被提醒也收效甚微。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 模型的这种偏见在工业和安全关键场景存在严重隐患。",
      "explanation": "在自动质检、医疗诊断等领域，AI 对罕见异常的误判可能导致产品缺陷、医疗事故，甚至危及生命安全，需要警惕其盲点。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "大模型，其实从来都没真的在看图片。是的，AI 们根本就没有用眼睛看世界，它们用的是记忆。",
    "AI 最终的输出，是它认为正确的东西，而不是它看到的东西。",
    "它会忽略掉那个多出来的第六根手指，因为它在 AI 的知识体系里，是一个不合理的、概率极低的存在。",
    "当 AI 偏见不断累积时，总有一天，这个小小的错误，会在某个关键节点上，引发致命的事故。",
    "或许，科技越是发达，我们越要清醒地认识到它的盲点。至少现在看来，在无尽的数据背后，AI 们仍然是盲目的。"
  ],
